act-text: 97 -->This shipping method available only for UAE but except some areas which is far from the city.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="98"><!-- react-text: 99 -->This shipping method is supported by NAX Express.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="100"><!-- react-text: 101 -->Not all warehouses support this shipping method; an alert will appear during checkout to notify users if the item is not eligible.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="102"><!-- react-text: 103 -->Not all orders qualify for this shipping method. Determination of eligibility will be made based on order weight and item dimensions.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="104"><!-- react-text: 105 -->This order methods not available for some promotional products; If order have extra charges for delivery, we will inform you during order creation or checkout time.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="106"><!-- react-text: 107 -->All orders may require 24-48 hours for the processing time before shipping.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="108"><!-- react-text: 109 -->dermowhitecream.com does not process orders during weekends.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="110"><!-- react-text: 111 -->No deliveries will be made on Fridays.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="112"><!-- react-text: 113 -->dermowhitecream.com does not guarantee same day shipping.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="114"><!-- react-text: 115 -->dermowhitecream.com does not offer International shipping options at this time.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="116"><!-- react-text: 117 -->Exact delivery times cannot be guaranteed.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="118"><!-- react-text: 119 -->dermowhitecream.com will NOT deal with or provide any services or products to OFAC sanctioned countries in accordance with the law of UAE.<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="120"><br data-reactid="121"><!-- react-text: 122 -->Orders<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="123"><br data-reactid="124"><!-- react-text: 125 -->Placi